headline: Carnival (CCL): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q1 Earnings?
summary: Carnival trades at $18.45 per share and has stayed right on track with the overall market, losing 11.8% over the last six months while the S&P 500 is down 8.1%. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
